data.description: This captivating 1979 ranch-style home boasts 5 bedrooms (one transformed into an expansive walk-in closet) and 2 remodeled baths. The kitchen and bathrooms showcase a modern blue/gray color palette. Revel in features like LVT flooring, stainless appliances, central air, and updated windows. Enjoy a distinctive view of the bluffs, along with raised garden beds, a chicken coop, raspberry bushes, shed, and a hunter's butcher shed.,Other highlights include RV parking on both sides, a new roof (2019), a dog door, and proximity to the esteemed Sweetwater 2 school district. Uncover a secret room for your special 2nd Amendment items and ample backyard space for recreational vehicles. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood with welcoming neighbors, this home is a true gem! Seize the opportunity with a remarkable 2.3% assumable (Veteran only) VA mortgage!  Call Annika Smith at 307-371-2535 to view this property today!!
